    <item>
      <title>Shoprite的利润攀升了14％的节奏，南非需求的增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/shoprite-profit-climbs-14-paced-by-rising-south-african-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ShopRite Holdings Ltd.的营业利润增长在上半年加速了，这有助于南非本国市场的需求不断上升，后者正在从使人衰弱的电力短缺中恢复过来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/shoprite-profit-climbs-14-paced-by-rising-south-african-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 06:22:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔的Gruenwald：关税无法解决我们的财政问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/s-p-s-gruenwald-tariffs-won-t-solve-us-fiscal-problems-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[S＆amp; P Global Ratings的首席经济学家Paul Gruenwald与彭博电视台的Joumanna Bercetche在地平线中东和非洲表演中进行了交谈。格鲁恩瓦尔德（Gruenwald）表示，特朗普的关税将“全面[…]负面”。他还谈到了税款如何导致墨西哥和加拿大的经济衰退，他们将首当其冲地关税和中国潜在的报复征税税。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-04/s-p-s-gruenwald-tariffs-won-t-solve-us-fiscal-problems-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 06:13:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Aramco削减了全球最大的股息，以打击沙特预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/aramco-cuts-world-s-biggest-dividend-in-blow-to-saudi-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿兰科（Aramco）削减了世界上最大的股息，这对沙特阿拉伯的预算赤字扩大，因为该公司试图释放自己的财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/aramco-cuts-world-s-biggest-dividend-in-blow-to-saudi-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 06:10:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着中国报复，美国主要的美国农业出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-puts-tariffs-on-us-soybean-corn-agricultural-commodities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为对华盛顿的对策的一部分，北京将对美国的一系列农产品征收关税，威胁要破坏两个农业强国之间的关键部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/china-puts-tariffs-on-us-soybean-corn-agricultural-commodities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:24:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级了全球贸易战，引发了山雀税率的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加了对加拿大和墨西哥的威胁，付出了巨大的进口征税，并对中国的现有指控增加了一倍，这激发了迅速报复，使世界经济陷入了深入的贸易战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国银行说，特朗普关税尚未降低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/thai-monetary-policy-robust-enough-to-face-trump-tariff-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国中央银行捍卫其货币政策立场，足以承受美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对贸易伙伴的最新关税的波动，这表明在上周的惊喜削减之后，它可能避免进一步缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/thai-monetary-policy-robust-enough-to-face-trump-tariff-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 04:03:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普绘制红线以阻止中国贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-draws-currency-red-line-for-pboc-with-manipulation-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对中国货币政策的评论正在加强中央银行的案子，即使面对迫在眉睫的贸易战，也要坚持其保持人民币稳定的战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-draws-currency-red-line-for-pboc-with-manipulation-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 03:57:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当投资者评估关税响应时，中国股票减少损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/chinese-stocks-fall-as-tariff-reality-outweighs-stimulus-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者认为该国对唐纳德·特朗普的关税的回应，中国股票的下降幅度下降了，这使人们对贸易紧张局势的全面升级升级的任何直接担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/chinese-stocks-fall-as-tariff-reality-outweighs-stimulus-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 01:39:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票鞭子，关税后石油下降：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税的回应后，股票弥补了损失，并避免了世界两大经济体之间的全面贸易战争。财政部的产量消除了，而石油下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 22:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
